       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                    WORKING STORAGE SECTION                     *
      ******************************************************************
       01  FILLER              PIC X(40) VALUE 'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE'.
      ******************************************************************
      * PROGRAM CONTROL
      ******************************************************************
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME              PIC  X(10) VALUE 'PSB4134'.

      ******************************************************************
      * ARQUITECTURA
